data.description: Indulge in the breathtaking and captivating lake views that define the charm of this remarkable pool home. Step inside to discover an open floor plan adorned with luxurious travertine tile and enhanced by new fixtures throughout. The heart of this home is its expansive and remodeled kitchen, with an abundance of cabinets and countertop space, ideal for both culinary enthusiasts and those who love to entertain. The bathrooms have been updated, featuring granite counters and custom showers that add a touch of elegance to the home. A custom travertine fireplace serves as a focal point, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. French doors open to the covered back patio and hot tub area. The patio is equipped with full remote-controlled electronic sun shades, providing privacy, protection, and a touch of style. The outdoor haven continues with a sparkling pool and an artificial turf area, creating a perfect oasis for relaxation and entertainment. You'll be enchanted by the outdoor living area, strategically placed to capture truly epic lake views and sunsets. The property also includes extra parking for Boats/RV, adding convenience to your lifestyle.
